<sect1 id=main-window>
<title>The Main Interface</title>
<para>PLACE HOLDER</para>
<para>The main window for &app; is the first window that opens when you launch &app;.</para>
<informalexample>
<para>
From the command line  type <programlisting>cronosII</programlisting>.
Alternatively launching with the help switch :<programlisting>cronosII --help</programlisting> will give you a list of options you may add when launching &app;. </para>
<para>Otherwise &app; will be found under Internet Applications or Perhaps Mailers on your Graphical User Interface Menus..</para>
</informalexample>

<sect2 id=the-window>
<title>The Main Window</title>
<para>Describe Main Window Layout and GTK</para>

