<sect2 id=main-filemenu>
<title>File Menu</title>

<para>Open this menu to work with individual messages and accounts.</para>
<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>New</para> <itemizedlist>
	  <listitem><para>Email </para>
	    <para>Select this to open the <link linkend=composer> Composer</link> and write a fresh Message</para></listitem>
	  <listitem><para>Mailbox</para>
	  <para>Select this to create a new mailbox.</para></listitem>
	  <listitem><para>Contact</para>
<para>Open the &app; Addressbook to add new listings .</para></listitem>
	 
	</itemizedlist></listitem>
<listitem><para>Check Mail</para><para>Select one or all of your accounts you would like to check  for mail.</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>Send Unsent Mail</para><para>Select this to send Mail waiting in your Mail Queue.</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>Address Book</para><para>Open the &app; Address Book </para></listitem>
<listitem><para>Save</para><para>Save the currently selected mail to a file</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>Print</para><para>Print the currently selected mail.</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>Exit</para><para>Close &app;. End this mail session.</para></listitem>

</itemizedlist>
</sect2>

